The obligation to publish a privacy notice in the context of personal data collection will not apply in relation to processing ‚Äúb
y a natural person in the course of a purely personal or household activity‚Äù (Reg 2(2)(c) GDPR). Your website might well fall within this exception ‚Äì although NB the European courts seem to be interpreting it narrowly.
